    <section class="section" id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>About OCD Car Detailing
            At OCD Car Detailing, we are passionate about perfection in automotive care. Specializing in meticulous detailing services, we go beyond the surface to restore your vehicle to its pristine condition. With a commitment to excellence, we offer a comprehensive range of services tailored to meet the highest standards of car enthusiasts and everyday drivers alike.
            
            Our Services Include:
            Paint Corrections: Using advanced techniques and premium products, we eliminate imperfections and restore the brilliance of your vehicle’s paint finish.
            
            Scratch Removal: Our skilled technicians delicately remove scratches and blemishes, ensuring a flawless exterior.
            
            Steaming for Upholstery: We employ state-of-the-art steam cleaning methods to effectively sanitize and rejuvenate your vehicle’s upholstery, leaving it fresh and immaculate.
            
            Carpet Shampooing: Deep cleaning of carpets and mats to remove embedded dirt and stains, enhancing both appearance and comfort.
            
            Headliner Detailing: Precision cleaning of headliners to remove dust, stains, and odors, ensuring a pristine interior environment.
            
            Engine Bay Surface Cleaning: Thorough cleaning and degreasing of the engine bay to enhance performance and prolong the life of engine components.
            
            Headlight Restoration: Restoration of cloudy or yellowed headlights to improve visibility and safety on the road.
            
            Why Choose Us?
            At OCD Car Detailing, we understand that every vehicle deserves the utmost care and attention. Our experienced team uses industry-leading techniques and eco-friendly products to deliver exceptional results. Whether you’re preparing for a special event, maintaining your daily driver, or restoring a classic car, we are dedicated to exceeding your expectations.
            
            Experience the difference with OCD Car Detailing—where passion meets precision in automotive detailing.</p>
        <p>Our services are tailored to meet the specific needs of each client, ensuring your vehicle receives the care it deserves.</p>
    </section>

